	(text_box "DESIGN NOTE:\n3V3 LDO total current needs to be lower than 5mA at startup:\nEEPROM read: 1mA\nPOWER OK LED: 0.65mA\nTPD4S480: 0.16mA\nLM2765: 0.13mA\nLTC7004: 0.05mA\nI²C pull-ups: ~~0.5mA\nADC resistors: 0.02mA\nAND gate: <0.01mA\nTotal ~~2.5mA < 5mA"
